These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
City: hannover, boston
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta
2 different pets are kept: pony, dog
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, milk
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| City       | boston       | hannover |
| Game         | canasta | mah-jongg  |
| Pet       | dog    | pony    |
| Beverage   | milk       | juice      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
City: marseilles, boston
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, red
2 different pets are kept: lizard, horse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, prince
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| City      | boston     | marseilles |
| Color           | light-blue | red      |
| Pet   | horse  | lizard      |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | prince     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, german
2 different pets are kept: horse, fish
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, architect
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is the architect##1
3. the japanese is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Flower      | daisy | iris  |
| Nationality          | japanese    | german   |
| Pet   | fish  | horse   |
| Job     | architect     | photographer |

