.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, swimming
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, azure
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Hobby           | video-games | skydiving     |
| Sport   | snowboarding          | swimming |
| Beverage           | fanta          | sprite    |
| Color     | azure            | blue       |

 